==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Romeward
<hw>Rome"ward</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending or directed toward Rome,
or toward the Roman Catholic Church.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To analyze the crisis in its Anglican rather than in its
<qex>Romeward</qex> aspect.</q> <rj><qau>Gladstone.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

